channel.title: Can't play
channel.description:
Well i've been trying to get around this but just can't. I pick a server and all and i make a name, and i log in, but before it fully logs in, it redirects me back to the login screen. :confused:
What exactly comes up: Error: T2 - 126,253,253 - 24,0,0 - 83,116,97,116,117,115,58,32,78,111,114,109,97,108,38,80,108,97,121,101,114,10,90,79
that... all on 1 line though. Someone please tell what this is and how to solve it
